@Q10.TaskManager.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5253

### Registro de usuario
POST {{Q10.TaskManager.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "User",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### Login
POST {{Q10.TaskManager.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### Acceder a endpoint protegido sin token (deber√≠a retornar 401)
GET {{Q10.TaskManager.Api_HostAddress}}/api/tasks
Accept: application/json

### Acceder a endpoint protegido con token (reemplazar TOKEN_AQUI con el token obtenido del login)
GET {{Q10.TaskManager.Api_HostAddress}}/api/tasks
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_AQUI

